languages.text: Малопонятный и неизученный минерал оказывает странное воздействие на органику, ускоряя ее рост во много раз. Магос Биологис еще не изучили его влияние на людей.

languages.text: This mysterious and unstudied mineral has a strange effect on organics, accelerating their growth many times over. The Magi Biologis have still not studied its effects on humans.

traits.locale_text: This mysterious mineral accelerates the growth of living organisms. The exact nature of this process is not yet clear and is a subject for Magos Biologis to study.
